            "description": "The integration invokes Lambda via aws_lambda_permission.allow_api_gateway with principal=apigateway.amazonaws.com. No authorization policy or API key is enforced on the HTTP API stage, allowing any external client to invoke the GET /users endpoint and trigger Lambda execution without authentication.",
