    "riskRationale": "The architecture exposes critical risks: unencrypted HTTP communication, overly permissive IAM policies granting unrestricted DynamoDB access, lack of API authentication, and missing audit controls; combined with the public-facing API Gateway and trust boundary between API and Lambda, attackers can eavesdrop, inject payloads, and exploit Lambda to read/write all user data with no rate limiting or recovery mechanisms.",
